CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 14, 1950, pg. 5, reads: "Teen-Agers Party - The Schenley Heights Teen-Agers held a very gay formal party recently at the Centre Avenue YWCA. Among those present were the above lovelies.  Left to right:  Delores Parker, Geraldine Williams, Jean Randall, Phyllis Harper, Menora Covenia and Nancy Foster.  Seated on the floor are Wilma Duncan and Barbara Griggs. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of members of "Schenley Heights Teen-Agers" back row from left: Delores Parker, Geraldine Williams, Jean Randall, Phyllis Harper, Menora Covenia, Nancy Foster; on floor: Wilma Duncan and Barbara Griggs, posed in front of Christmas tree in YMCA or YWCA
